We can pay you a total of 30,000 yen.

01:18.125 --> 01:19.292
"Bank"

01:19.959 --> 01:21.959
I'll be withdrawing everything.

01:25.049 --> 01:27.227
"I'll pay back your money"

01:58.117 --> 02:00.177
"The last day"

