54:32.501 --> 54:34.584
What?

54:34.751 --> 54:36.167
I... I have

54:36.250 --> 54:37.709
something to ask of you.

54:38.250 --> 54:40.501
Do you know the phone number
or something to contact

54:40.626 --> 54:43.334
