55:12.209 --> 55:13.375
Hey!

55:13.792 --> 55:15.501
Here we are!

55:17.209 --> 55:18.542
My sis says

55:18.667 --> 55:22.375
She's pissed at you since you are looking
for a old classmate without her.

55:22.501 --> 55:25.167
