56:40.876 --> 56:42.459
Do you remember me?

56:43.209 --> 56:44.918
Hello!

56:45.042 --> 56:47.125
Huh? Ishida-kun?

56:48.375 --> 56:49.417
Heh heh heh.

56:50.167 --> 56:52.159
Long time no see.

56:57.042 --> 57:00.584
I continued to study sign language after that.

57:01.083 --> 57:02.667
