01:09:01.082 --> 01:09:03.542
Hey! Stop doing that over my head!

01:09:03.667 --> 01:09:05.959
Miyo-chan, long time no see.

01:09:06.082 --> 01:09:08.125
By the way, where is Nishimiya today?

01:09:08.250 --> 01:09:09.876
