01:09:36.917 --> 01:09:37.917
Oh,

01:09:38.292 --> 01:09:39.792
That's a good idea.

01:09:43.417 --> 01:09:44.716
(From: Ishida)
"We are planning to go to the amusement park,"

01:09:44.716 --> 01:09:46.716
